videos.description: Devin Vassell's momentum takes him behind the backboard as he's being fouled, but he swishes home the jump shot anyway.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (FSU's Vassell sinks and-1 jumper from behind backboard) 2020/01/08

videos.headline: FSU's Vassell sinks and-1 jumper from behind backboard

videos.description: Wake Forest's Jahcobi Neath can't convert at the rim in transition, but Olivier Sarr corrals the miss and slams it home.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Wake's Sarr flushes putback slam with authority) 2020/01/08

videos.headline: Wake's Sarr flushes putback slam with authority

videos.description: Brandon Childress slings a left-handed bounce pass to Isaiah Mucius in transition for an easy dunk, giving Wake Forest the lead over Florida State.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Childress drops dime to Mucius for Wake Forest slam) 2020/01/08

videos.headline: Childress drops dime to Mucius for Wake Forest slam
